Package: formula1data
Type: Package
Title: Imports Formula 1 Data using the 'Ergast' API
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alex Kraieski
Maintainer: Alex Kraieski <arkraieski@gmail.com>
Description: An R wrapper for the 'Ergast' API. It has functions to import Formula 1 lap times, pit stops, qualifying results, race results, and championship standings.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Imports: lubridate (>= 1.7.4), dplyr (>= 0.8.0.1), tidyr (>= 0.8.3), httr, jsonlite, rlang, RSQLite (>= 2.2.0), DBI, purrr, duckdb
